8. Check clearance height of combination of Schlepper and Maschine.
9. Lower hydraulic jack if needed.
10. Lock the lever of the hydraulic jack during transport to prevent unintentional sinking of a drawn machine.
11. Control function of lighting.
12. Check if dosing units are closed.
13. Turn off control panel.
14. Remove any dirt that could be dropped and pollute the road, as it poses a danger to users.
